title: No doom bots Icon Received over 1 week +
body:
Hey Just wondering why I haven't received my doom bots icon yet for defeating doom bots on the 20/10/16 

Other friends have received theirs and I'm just wondering if its been a glitch or something :)

How would I go about getting the icon on my account? do I need to submit a support ticket?

Proof: http://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/OC1/151223005/200832467?tab=overview

More Proof: http://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/OC1/152762438/200832467?tab=overview

replies.body:
Hey there,

Your best bet in this situation would be to [submit a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) to Player Support as we here on the boards are unable to assist with account specific inquiries.
I don't mind waiting for it as long as I get it
As I said, you'll have to contact Player Support in regard to this matter.
